title: Total Drama Gone Wild
description: 19 contestants are brought to a tropical island named "Ciphoko Island" situated somewhere in eastern Europe with no WiFi or cellular reception. Once there they must survive a series of life risking challenges and threatening races with their fellow enemies or friends to be the only one left standing on the island to win $1,000,000! So once again watch (and laugh) as teen freaks, geeks & egos crash, smash & bash their way to victory! Who will win? And who will go home first? Find out in Total Drama Gone Wild!
